{"tid":523694,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人3月去大阪？ 入嚟比啲意見","createTime":"2018-01-08T22:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T11:35:31.000Z","uid":116257,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c80c7e6a390968b83d9b335de337b7f499b887e0","tid":523694,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T22:44:51.000Z","msg":"如題！我就3月尾到去，應該玩8-9日<br />\n<br />\n諗緊關西落機先去京都玩 還是先玩大阪一兩日再去京都玩然後又返回大阪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n京都嗰邊會去嵐山同稻田神社，清水寺裝修諗緊去唔去好（逛下二三年坂好唔好）<br />\n<br />\n大阪都係天守閣，心齋，黑門，環球影城嗰堆<br />\n<br />\n周遊券諗緊買 ICOCA &amp; HARUKA + 大阪二日遊券好定 關西廣域周遊券+ 大阪二日遊券<br />\n<br />\n第一次去，求比啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e97e6f9f0525d0bc634f0790f557d4f6e24a5a3","tid":523694,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T23:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f41b55956ee5a3c48fa95a078762d898451067","tid":523694,"uid":52929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:52:38.000Z","msg":"3月去大板 但係咩都未plan 淨係睇左機票都5千7"},{"pid":"6b684b5b5ada8a8284e444b4d059a8a07d67d02d","tid":523694,"uid":52929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22f41b55956ee5a3c48fa95a078762d898451067","tid":523694,"uid":52929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:52:38.000Z","msg":"3月去大板 但係咩都未plan 淨係睇左機票都5千7"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:53:16.000Z","msg":"兩個人來回"},{"pid":"98d066593d9f0a592113a59248ddd074aa88e47a","tid":523694,"uid":69064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b684b5b5ada8a8284e444b4d059a8a07d67d02d","tid":523694,"uid":52929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22f41b55956ee5a3c48fa95a078762d898451067","tid":523694,"uid":52929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:52:38.000Z","msg":"3月去大板 但係咩都未plan 淨係睇左機票都5千7"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-