月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:29:35.000Z","msg":"3月尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486f27d905e9cecf027fddc58e3e6c5792cec9bb","tid":523694,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71d868dd67718bca598a37bc3dbe4890bdb8a2c2","tid":523694,"uid":150736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:24:15.000Z","msg":"我都係3月尾去 機票一人5500<br />\n都預去USJ 黑門市場 神戶 奈良 京都<br />\n實際點行就未plan"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:31:40.000Z","msg":"有料！"},{"pid":"96f7aa65a68a15641f9e8164d5ecd5bd78e7bc1a","tid":523694,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6389bcfa695950d99903ec244fe300c724bb0ceb","tid":523694,"uid":71058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:25:27.000Z","msg":"來來去去都係果D架啦 <br />\nPLAN 乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:32:38.000Z","msg":"第一次點都要撚手準備嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48bf70a4d05e2b49b22d3c1fd5386b64c7a3eaa","tid":523694,"uid":78770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:38:08.000Z","msg":"去京都就不如去埋奈良啦<br />\n你奈良用一日<br />\n京都可以2-4日 (睇下你自己鐘唔鐘意行古蹟)<br />\n鐘意shopping嘅就大阪可以留耐少少"},{"pid":"788563e631d7d93fd0697962f28d557f1d69283e","tid":523694,"uid":92201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:38:12.000Z","msg":"去一轉大阪要5500????商務啊?<br />\n<br />\n你有8-9日, 抽一兩日去六甲山浸下溫泉都好"},{"pid":"077d6cb5ce5172f4a68586be69f50b407288b3a1","tid":523694,"uid":138313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"千本櫻"},{"pid":"53536e122139a84469075ef2faf7aea3b121353c","tid":523694,"uid":78770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e48bf70a4d05e2b49b22d3c1fd5386b64c7a3eaa","tid":523694,"uid":78770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:38:08.000Z","msg":"去京都就不如去埋奈良啦<br />\n你奈良用一日<br />\n京都可以2-4日 (睇下你自己鐘唔鐘意行古蹟)<br />\n鐘意shopping嘅就大阪可以留耐少少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:41:50.000Z","msg":"舊年去<br />\n玩左好似都玩左8日<br />\n3日京都加奈良 時間就好趕 好多野都係就咁睇一睇就算 冇咩深入咁去睇<br />\n可以試下著下和服行 都係一個幾好嘅體驗<br />\n之後USJ留一日時間 可以唔洗買fast pass就咁排都唔係話要排好耐<br />\n周遊卷真係好睇你自己點plan時間<br />\n我就買左ICOCA &amp; HARUKA 用 冇買過周遊卷<br />\n同埋我自己住南船場 行10分鐘就到心齋橋 去好多地方都係用IC卡平過用周遊卷 所以先冇買<br />\n<br />\n如果想睇櫻花 不如就4月頭先去<br />\n3月尾真係要好好彩先有"},{"pid":"7968bf50e27235603ce5914daa9584382447d976","tid":523694,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:46:32.000Z","msg":"清水寺果邊 多人過旺角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去完實好後悔，撞正夜晚點燈反而好d"},{"pid":"2b6714544302df119977d45196127187aaafbfb9","tid":523694,"uid":26468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"423baff925a1f05cbf6447fc8f515c9909613d8d","tid":523694,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3c98f58463179e67a34a337c66447aa647153a7","tid":523694,"uid":26468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c80c7e6a390968b83d9b335de337b7f499b887e0","tid":523694,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T22:44:51.000Z","msg":"如題！我就3月尾到去，應該玩8-9日<br />\n<br />\n諗緊關西落機先去京都玩 還是先玩大阪一兩日再去京都玩然後又返回大阪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n京都嗰邊會去嵐山同稻田神社，清水寺裝修諗緊去唔去好（逛下二三年坂好唔好）<br />\n<br />\n大阪都係天守閣，心齋，黑門，環球影城嗰堆<br />\n<br />\n周遊券諗緊買 ICOCA &amp; HARUKA + 大阪二日遊券好定 關西廣域周遊券+ 大阪二日遊券<br />\n<br />\n第一次去，求比啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:26:26.000Z","msg":"你有無tg 我都3月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:29:35.000Z","msg":"3月尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:59:22.000Z","msg":"中"},{"pid":"89c6578bb892380f0ba7628a1e86779dc2b70a49","tid":523694,"uid":11717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:02:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清水寺果邊 多人過旺角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去完實好後悔，撞正夜晚點燈反而好d</blockquote><br />\n京都大阪邊度都多人架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45dfbf8ebbfe81762b0e91a00e2ef66987036ce","tid":523694,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89c6578bb892380f0ba7628a1e86779dc2b70a49","tid":523694,"uid":11717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:02:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清水寺果邊 多人過旺角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去完實好後悔，撞正夜晚點燈反而好d</blockquote><br />\n京都大阪邊度都多人架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:33:02.000Z","msg":"唔係果隻多，係可以逼到好似維港倒數既隻多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0cfb6ce818531cf9a258936d9e114b468d7601b","tid":523694,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c45dfbf8ebbfe81762b0e91a00e2ef66987036ce","tid":523694,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89c6578bb892380f0ba7628a1e86779dc2b70a49","tid":523694,"uid":11717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:02:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清水寺果邊 多人過旺角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去完實好後悔，撞正夜晚點燈反而好d</blockquote><br />\n京都大阪邊度都多人架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:33:02.000Z","msg":"唔係果隻多，係可以逼到好似維港倒數既隻多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:41:24.000Z","msg":"同意 個心齋橋都同銅鑼灣冇分別 多撚人到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"